Package: photobiologySensors
Type: Package
Title: Spectral Response Data for Light Sensors
Version: 0.4.0
Date: 2018-02-26
Authors@R:
   c(
    person("Pedro J.", "Aphalo", email = "pedro.aphalo@helsinki.fi", role = c("aut", "cre"), comment = c(ORCID = "https://orcid.org/0000-0003-3385-972X"))
    )
Maintainer: Pedro J. Aphalo <pedro.aphalo@helsinki.fi>
Description: Spectral response data for broadband 
    ultraviolet and visible radiation sensors. These data are complemented by 
    data for the temperature response of one ultraviolet radiation sensor.
    Different data sources were used, author-supplied data from scientific 
    research papers, sensor-manufacturer supplied data, and published sensor
    specifications. Part of the 'r4photobiology' suite 
    <Aphalo P. J. (2015) <doi:10.19232/uv4pb.2015.1.14>>.
License: GPL (>= 2)
VignetteBuilder: knitr
Depends:
    R (>= 3.3.0),
    photobiology (>= 0.9.18)
Suggests:
    knitr (>= 1.19),
    photobiologyWavebands (>= 0.4.2),
    ggspectra (>= 0.2.2),
    ggplot2 (>= 2.2.1)
LazyLoad: yes
LazyData: yes
ByteCompile: true
Encoding: UTF-8
URL: http://www.r4photobiology.info, https://bitbucket.org/aphalo/photobiologysensors
